{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/About_en.png?t=1737398221\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unleash your Animal Instincts!!!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Banner_Combat.gif?t=1737398221\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Faunamorph</strong></i> is a 2D metroidvania set in an abandoned underground lab, where you can recombine your own DNA to transform parts of your body into animals limbs. Use the brute strength of a rhino\u2019s horn to break walls, glide over pits with bird wings, and dig tunnels on the ground with mole claws to travel through the laboratory and uncover it\u2019s dark secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Banner_WallJump.png?t=1737398221\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Gameplay_en.png?t=1737398221\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Shape-Shifting Mastery</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Banner_DNA_Combine.gif?t=1737398221\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harness the power of animal genetics as you transform your body into incredible animal forms, acquiring new abilities to overcome obstacles and uncover the truth. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Banner_Freezing.png?t=1737398221\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Change your DNA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Banner_OctopusRhino.gif?t=1737398221\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adapt on the fly by equipping and swapping abilities, strategically selecting your arsenal of animal powers to suit each challenge and unlock new paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Banner_CryoTube.png?t=1737398221\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Uncover your Origins</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Banner_Trampoline.png?t=1737398221\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an immersive journey through the dark corridors and hidden chambers of the abandoned lab, piecing together the puzzle of Project H.A.G.E.N's mysterious experiments and your own forgotten past.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Banner_WalkingResearch.png?t=1737398221\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461980/extras/Features_en.png?t=1737398221\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master your Helix Space by recombining your DNA, switching out your animal abilities on the fly for different combat and exploration scenarios.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Transform your body with unique animal abilities, from rolling like an armadillo to swimming like a dolphin, each tailored to overcome new challenges and explore deeper into the lab.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face off against twisted hulking hybrids, failed experiments and self-defense systems, while testing your skills and powers in creative, intense encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover lore-rich data logs scattered throughout the abandoned lab, revealing the purpose of Project H.A.G.E.N. and the origins of the terrifying hybrid creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a dynamic soundtrack that adapts to your journey, with moods shifting from intense combat to ominous exploration and frenetic survival in near-death moments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock a sprawling, interconnected world with rooms to discover and hidden upgrades, adding replayability as you uncover every corner of the lab.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Roll with It","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/ee32129be4553d597c0d91e70681609a0483c2eb.jpg"},{"name":"Falling with Style","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/bd4906a650b54616b87b75238a2e4b9d5f3ccd72.jpg"},{"name":"Wave Rider","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/7d57555c4d477000c7a40146694bf07b1545a839.jpg"},{"name":"Glow Up","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/e840efbaa1254a833cbee69d00e044b7ba61109f.jpg"},{"name":"Jump Start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/7a0cfbce68955a1081de04ab156ffac246723abc.jpg"},{"name":"Leap of Faith","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/155a1e90b9afb6be45e7ea956859bc625c372547.jpg"},{"name":"Just Keep Digging","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/fb8df97c2f5e2b7f7c109a04cba613bb107bd7f0.jpg"},{"name":"Swing into Action","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/101b88de067b83c958a359871024134c3dd69c89.jpg"},{"name":"Cephalopower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2461980/259e3025f2818be5c152cef77420f89722d328e3.jpg"},{"name":"Charge Ahead","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.c